Market Segments:


Federal Government
Building facilities throughout the world in austere and remote locations.


Commercial & Industrial
Providing construction services both locally and globally as BE&K Building Group.


Power
A global provider of turn-key power generation services.














Pernix Group is a leading construction company offering diversified general contracting, design-build and construction management services to private clients and public agencies. 
We have provided construction services since 1995 and have established a strong reputation within the Government, Commercial & Industrial, and Power markets by executing complex projects on-time and within budget while adhering to strict quality control measures. We are well known for successfully completing large, complex construction projects for government agencies and private clients throughout the world and in some of the most challenging remote environments. 


learn more












SAFETY FIRST
Dedicated to providing a safe and healthy workplace for all employees, subcontractor personnel and building occupants.
learn more








SUSTAINABILITY
Protecting the environment is part of our core culture. We incorporate specific measures into the planning of every project to minimize our environmental impact.
learn more








Performance Excellence
Pernix is driven by its commitment for performance excellence. We are agile and adept at quickly understanding and adapting to the client’s needs. 
