Services
Our Work









Home  /  Our Work  /  Services 








Pernix Group is a leading construction company, offering diversified general contracting, design/build, construction management, pre-construction consulting, EPC, and O&M services to private clients and public agencies throughout the world.














Pre-construction Consulting

                                    Our Work                                


Our early-on management approach aligns the best resources for all aspects of every project. Our field-tested approach works in conjunction with our customer’s needs and expectations to develop a plan and an execution schedule that saves time and money while ensuring timely and successful completion of the customer's project.
see page








Construction Management (Risk & Agency)

                                    Our Work                                


Our state-of-the-art Construction Management services will provide a systematic project review, including a comprehensive construction and start-up schedule.
see page








Engineering, Procurement & Construction

                                    Our Work                                


Pernix Group delivers projects in short time frames while ensuring safety and quality. We manage project costs while driving productivity
see page








General Contracting

                                    Our Work                                


Pernix Group acts as a general contractor on projects where we have responsibility from award through the successful completion of the project.
see page








Design-Build

                                    Our Work                                


Pernix embraces the design/build model to ensure design excellence and successful completion of construction projects from analysis, architecture, and permitting through engineering, construction, and completion.
see page








Operations & Maintenance

                                    Our Work                                


Pernix Group’s Power Operations and Maintenance Services (O&M) provide an integrated scope of services to effectively maintain and manage all aspects of power operations.
see page





















 



