Pernix Group Inc.


            
            Pernix Group, Inc. is a construction company, which offers general contracting, design and build, construction management, preconstruction consulting, EPC, and O&M services to private clients and public agencies. It operates through the following segments: Construction, Power Services, and Corporate. The Construction segment includes general contracting and construction management services. The Power Services segment comprises of plant engineering, procurement, and construction; operations and maintenance services; and build, own, operate, transfer capabilities. The Corporate segment covers the indirect activities that support the construction and power businesses of the firm. The company was founded by Nidal Z. Zayed in 1994 and is headquartered in Lombard, IL.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  



 


